By this point I am pissing myself because how freaked out I am when suddenly the most terrifying thing appeared. Down the street I see the Cheeto man (aka Donald trump) holding a bag of Cheetos who are his distant relatives, sprinting towards me, laughing like a complete and utter psychopath. Then, my phone reopened this app without me doing anything and once it opened it made Donald trump even more of a mad man as he looked right to where I was in the tree when finally I come to my senses and exited this app once more and deleted it and everything when back to normal. So overall, I would highly suggest not downloading this app for your own good.
